items.name: Lethal Pride
explicitMods:
Commanded leadership over 17546 warriors under Kaom
Passives in radius are Conquered by the Karui
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: They believed themselves the greatest warriors, but that savagery turned upon their own.

items.name: Watcher's Eye
explicitMods: +7% chance to Evade Attack Hits while affected by Grace
40% increased Cooldown Recovery Rate of Movement Skills used while affected by Haste
+14% chance to Suppress Spell Damage while affected by Grace
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: One by one, they stood their ground against a creature
they had no hope of understanding, let alone defeating,
and one by one, they became a part of it.

items.name: The Green Nightmare
explicitMods: Gain 7% of Cold Damage as Extra Chaos Damage

Passives granting Cold Resistance or all Elemental Resistances in Radius
also grant Chance to Suppress Spell Damage at 70% of its value
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: We take root in the dirt
and strangle those who tread upon it.

items.name: Ancestral Vision
explicitMods: Modifiers to Chance to Suppress Spell Damage also apply to Chance to Avoid Elemental Ailments at 50% of their Value
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The spirits of our ancestors guided us from the Archipelago to the continent.
Inextricably, the purity of our souls is linked to the ones who came before us.
